title: The Supernaturalist
author: Eoin Colfer
genre: Fiction, Young Adult, Science Fiction / Fantasy
description: A young adult science fiction novel set in a dystopian future where 14‑year‑old Cosmo Hill escapes from an oppressive hospital and joins a group called the Supernaturalists — kids who hunt blue, ghost‑like creatures called Parasites. They soon uncover secrets about their world, confronting corporate corruption, moral dilemmas, and the nature of life and death in a fast‑paced, action‑packed story.
